{"type": "article", "id": 57349, "title": "旺旺与自然堂合作面膜，78% 美国广告主协会成员自建广告部门 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-10-16T04:24:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 14249, "name": "印度市场"}, {"id": 295, "name": "跨界"}, {"id": 25016, "name": "旺旺"}, {"id": 30110, "name": "自然堂"}, {"id": 329, "name": "宝洁"}, {"id": 3934, "name": "NFL"}, {"id": 13165, "name": "Grey"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1375, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181016112202kSo75rZu6PX1InAc.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4295458027151638?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=108A093010&amp;sourcetype=weixin\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>旺旺 x 自然堂</strong></a>合作了雪饼气垫+旺旺局部面膜，售价暂时未知。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181016110536UksgZMQJ6vxa0Weu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.532394\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4295672528545168\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>百威 x&nbsp;PRIVATE POLICY</strong></a> 推出联名款服饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201810161108412AUzSt0RIKgOemL3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181016110841SH4otDduGLkNRChc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181016110841k7q0mieQpnhKY5Ga.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/pantene-in-japan-launches-new-advertising-campaign-called-freedom-in-job-hunting-leveraging-real-intentions-of-1-000-university-students-300730747.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>潘婷在日本发起新的 campaign <em>#Freedom in Job-Hunting</em></strong></a>，鼓励求职季的女性不再绑马尾辫，更多用发型展示自己。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=z0749jd4sgl\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/10/15/ikea-india-brings-its-lamps-life-with-talking-products-ad-campaign\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>进驻印度市场后，宜家发起了 <em>Talking Products</em> 为主题的新 campaign</strong></a>，主角是一堆会说话的家具。每支广告片标题都是“不同于其他家具（椅子/储物柜/台灯/书架）”，强调其与其他家具在设计上的不同，也更人性化。代理商为&nbsp;Dentsu Impact。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l0749s0auzh\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l0749krrjgk\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b0749cgk7l3\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=o0749kra9ps\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p>Swatch 继续“经典新生”主题的 campaign，<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4295496517979709\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>找来昆曲传人黄亚男拍摄新的广告片</strong></a>，把昆曲与说唱放在了一起<strong>。</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t0749wkhjja\"></iframe> </figure> </div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/the-nfl-places-its-advertising-business-in-review-after-10-years-with-grey/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>NFL 正在考虑撤换目前合作 10 年的代理商 Grey。</strong></a>Adweek 援引信源消息称，在咨询公司 Roth Ryan Hayes 负责的一次比稿中，NFL 将其接触的 12 家代理商削减至 7 家。Grey 自 2009 年开始负责 NFL 的媒介、服饰品牌等业务。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/ana-report-in-housing-agency-work-is-accelerating/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国广告主协会发布调研报告称，该协会 78% 的成员自建广告部门。</strong></a>2008、2013 年的调研报告中，该比例分别为 42%、58%。今年新的调研报告中，44% 的协会成员称其在过去 5 年中组建了内部广告部门。</p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：YouTube@<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Y3L26yB9I0ygLnnCcbWHQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">PANTENE Japan Official</a></p>"}